e deduction of the\noutside appearance of hot bare strange stars, which might help discern them\nfrom neutron stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 31 Aug 2003 08:29:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Mar 2004 08:42:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
